dismissalText.commentary: Prosper Utseya c Porterfield b van der Merwe 12 (13b 1x4 0x6 16m) SR: 92.3

dismissalComment.html: tried to chip short mid wicket but could not have enough bat to it and he was caught

commentTextItems.html: sliced the ball into the hands of Dockrell, throws it back but misses the stumps
block hole dugged out down to deep mid on
drove to mid off and a quick single ; fielder hits the stumps but Cremer is safe
inside edge between keeper and short fine leg
punched into the covers no run
guided well into the hands of short third man, but managed to squeze for a single and an over throw and they came back for the second
gave himself some room past with point to third man
